### ================== RUTAS SIN AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los prescription medicines (SIN token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines/public

### Obtener prescription medicine por ID (SIN token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines/public/1

### Crear un nuevo prescription medicine (SIN token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prescription_id": 1,
  "medicine_id": 2,
  "dosage": "2 tablets",
  "duration": "7 days",
  "instructions": "Take after meals"
}

### Actualizar un prescription medicine (SIN token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines/public/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dosage": "1 tablet",
  "duration": "5 days",
  "instructions": "Take before meals"
}

### Eliminar un prescription medicine (SIN token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines/public/1

### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los prescription medicines (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener prescription medicine por ID (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un nuevo prescription medicine (CON token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prescription_id": 2,
  "medicine_id": 3,
  "dosage": "1 capsule",
  "duration": "10 days",
  "instructions": "Take with water"
}

### Actualizar un prescription medicine (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dosage": "2 capsules",
  "duration": "14 days",
  "instructions": "Take with food"
}

### Eliminar un prescription medicine (CON token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/prescription-medicines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
